INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (8,4,'2019-09-09 14:59:29','2019-09-09 14:59:29','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":9} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://polarprod.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/shutterstock_1023594121.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Drum, weâre happy when our Drummers are happy. Drummers are the engine room of our platform, and we want to be your support staff as you find new opportunities to earn money, develop sales skills and build your brand.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As you begin your Drummer journey, here are some unique traits that set the best Drummers apart:<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1. Knowledge about Drum</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drummers with substantial knowledge about our platform, the business, and the promotions have higher success rates. You should:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Know the business</li><li>Know the promotion</li><li>Know the Drum platform</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Take the time to get to know who youâre representing. You will be more comfortable with the business and better able to explain its value confidently. A sale is more likely when a Drummer has the details their potential buyer needs. Research what companies inside of your space or other Drummers in your area are doing, too!<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2. Organization</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drummers need to manage buyers, their schedules, and their modes of communication. Organization will help you keep track of your progress to better estimate your compensation. Only then can you spot unresolved issues or plans no longer relevant to your business.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>3. Social Observance</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Socially-observant Drummers can connect with many different types of people! Be conscious of your potential buyer and your environment. Some helpful tips include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Be mindful of your opinions and humor</li><li>Pay attention to subtle verbal, non-verbal, and behavioral cues</li><li>Give buyers time to think before signing on with Drum</li><li>Be aware of your tone to avoid being rude or pushy</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>4. Active Listening Skills</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before talking to your potential buyer about Drum, listen to what they are saying.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Inquire about their concerns. This will encourage your buyer to drop their guard and genuinely open up to you. You will be more likely to address how your business will satisfy their needs.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>5. Empathy</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By listening to your buyer, youâre more likely to make a connection with them. Be sure to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Identify with your buyerâs feelings and frustrations without necessarily agreeing with them</li><li>Demonstrate your legitimate interest in providing your promotion as a solution</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>6. Striving for Repeat Business</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drummers who make secure connections with their buyers open the door to future business. The lifetime value of a buyerâs trust is higher than that of a quick sale.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>7. Curiosity</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drummers are curious and excited about Drum, the businesses they promote, and reaching new buyers. They are competitive by nature, measuring their skills against other Drummers around them.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>8. A Goal-Oriented Mindset</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Turn your motivation into action! First, get comfortable with working on a commission.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Set goals within your own limits. Make them achievable with persistence and hard work. This drive will enable you to solve issues for buyers as quickly and efficiently as possible.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>9. Persistence</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A Drummersâ job doesnât stop when one promotion is redeemed. Here are some essential ways of doing this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>If you can, follow up after a redemption to build an ongoing relationship with your buyer</li><li>Donât give up on buyers who have said no in the past</li><li>Adapt to buyersâ schedules and preferences</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But donât force it! Let Buyers know itâs okay to say no. While you shouldnât give up on Buyers who have said no in the past, know when itâs time to move on - and remember, donât take rejection personally! Itâs all part of the journey.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>10. Passion</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you love what you are selling, it is easier for you to represent and sell. This will empower you to work for more than just a quota.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drum is a platform for representing the businesses you believe in! Be passionate about making a change in peopleâs lives by giving them promotions and access to new experiences.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Drummers: The 10 Qualities of the Best Drummers','','publish','open','open','','drummers-the-10-qualities-of-the-best-drummers','','','2019-09-09 15:01:33','2019-09-09 15:01:33','',0,'http://polarprod.wpengine.com/?p=8',0,'post','',0),(9,4,'2019-09-09 14:47:59','2019-09-09 14:47:59','','shutterstock_1023594121','','inherit','open','closed','','shutterstock_1023594121','','','2019-09-09 14:47:59','2019-09-09 14:47:59','',8,'http://polarprod.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/shutterstock_1023594121.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(10,4,'2019-09-09 14:58:59','2019-09-09 14:58:59','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":11} -->\r\n<figure></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-11\" src=\"https://polarprod.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/shutterstock_372396238-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Our platform gives you unparalleled flexibility in creating campaigns to acquire customers. Below are some things to think about as your create your first offer, and some guidance on how the platform is built to help deliver success.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>What is my objective?</em></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Depending on where your business is in its growth journey, the <strong>type of offer</strong> your select can help meet your objectives. Some examples for each offer type are included below:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Savings offer:</span></strong> If you are growing and want to get more customers to try your product or service, offering an upfront savings is an enticing way to get customers in the door.</li>\r\n<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Loyalty offer:</span></strong> If you want to improve the quality of your customer base, a loyalty offer can increase repeat business and keep good customers coming back for more.</li>\r\n<li><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Referral request:</span></strong> Maybe this isnât the right time to offer a discount - no worries! A referral request incentivizes your Drummers to talk up your business and drive customers your way.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>What makes my business different and special?</em></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Youâve worked hard to define your brand, and we appreciate that entrusting your Drummers with this can feel daunting. In the âNotes for Drummersâ, you can provide helpful information and links to inform Drummers about what makes you special to ensure that they are well equipped to communicate that to prospective customers.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>Who is my target audience?</em></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Looking for a specific audience? You can either guide your Drummers on who the right personas are that you want to find, or even tailor your offers to a particular zip code that covers your target market.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>What is the right commission to set?</em></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Drum gives you flexibility in setting whatever commission you want and changing it any time. However, Drummers will be more incentivized to promote your products if there is a higher commission.Â </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>With this in mind, we typically encourage businesses to set a higher commission initially, and adjust this downwards as they see the redemptions come through. Remember, unlike most digital marketing tools, you are only paying a commission when you successfully acquire a new customer - so keep the âlifetimeâÂ value of aÂ  typical customer to your business in mind when setting your commission.Â </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>What is my budget?</em></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Drum allows you to âcapâ your total redemptions for a particular offer to fit your budget. You can set a maximum limit for the total number of redemptions or the total dollar amount that you want to spend for your campaign. This allows you to allocate your budget to different offers, and you can even test a few different types of offers to see what works best!</p>\r\n<p><em>How do I get started?</em></p>\r\n<p>Creating an offer is easy and takes just minutes! Simply follow the instructions included in the video link below:</p>\r\n<p>[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yHvD4wauxJg[/embed]</p>\r\n<p>Still have questions? Set up a conversations with one of our Offer Consultants at the link <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MyR6rA\">here</a>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Businesses: What to consider as you create your first offer','','publish','open','open','','businesses-what-to-consider-as-your-create-your-first-offer','','','2019-10-13 13:55:48','2019-10-13 13:55:48','',0,'http://polarprod.wpengine.com/?p=10',0,'post','',0),(11,4,'2019-09-09 14:50:21','2019-09-09 14:50:21','','shutterstock_372396238','','inherit','open','closed','','shutterstock_372396238','','','2019-09-09 14:50:21','2019-09-09 14:50:21','',10,'http://polarprod.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/shutterstock_372396238.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(12,4,'2019-09-09 14:59:50','2019-09-09 14:59:50','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":13} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Inspired by the advice of social media influencer in sales and entrepreneurship Gary Vaynerchuk, letâs talk about how you can answer the question: Why should your buyer listen to you?</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Start by filtering for what defines your personal brand.Â </strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Flooded with new information, products, and possibilities, Drum gives you the ability to pick out businesses that reflect on your personality &amp; interests.Â </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Start by thinking about products &amp; services you enjoy and would use personally, and use that as inspiration for selecting businesses you want to Drum for. Though you should aim to choose a business that champions who you are, this may not always be possible at the very start of your Drumming. If this is the case, reach out to those businesses and encourage them to be a partner of yours in joining the platform!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>When you Drum for products &amp; services you would personally, understanding what makes them special and communicating their value proposition to your Buyers becomes that much easier!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Use your identity and personal story to bring your products to life.</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Sales is about storytelling, and finding brands and businesses that resonate with your personal story helps bring these products and experiences to life for your Buyers.Â </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>So whether itâs that great wedding venue that made your special day so incredible, or that project management tool that made you so much more productive at work, your stories will provide a vision for how what youâre Drumming for can positively impact the lives of others.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Use your personal Drum catalog to build your personal brand.</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The businesses you are Drumming for will also reflect back on what is important to you - whether that is a passion for quality, advocacy for local businesses, or anything else, you can tailor your promotions to shine a light on what you love and value.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>How can Drum help build your brand in-person?</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Drum is a flexible, human-driven channel for exploring who you are. Drum empowers buyers to follow suit and build their own personal stories because they found value in yours.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Drummers: The Essential Guide to Drumming to Build Your Brand.','','publish','open','open','','drummers-the-essential-guide-to-drumming-to-build-your-brand','','','2019-09-27 03:03:31','2019-09-27 03:03:31','',0,'http://polarprod.wpengine.com/?p=12',0,'post','',0),(13,4,'2019-09-09 14:52:50','2019-09-09 14:52:50','','shutterstock_342602405','','inherit','open','closed','','shutterstock_342602405','','','2019-09-09 14:52:50','2019-09-09 14:52:50','',12,'http://polarprod.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/shutterstock_342602405.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(24,2,'2019-09-17 12:34:03','2019-09-17 12:34:03','a:7:{s:8:\"location\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:4:\"page\";}}}s:8:\"position\";s:6:\"normal\";s:5:\"style\";s:8:\"seamless\";s:15:\"label_placement\";s:3:\"top\";s:21:\"instruction_placement\";s:5:\"label\";s:14:\"hide_on_screen\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}','Page Settings','page-settings','publish','closed','closed','','group_5d695944b1575','','','2019-09-17 12:34:03','2019-09-17 12:34:03','',0,'http://polarprod.wpengine.com/?p=24',0,'acf-field-group','',0),(25,2,'2019-09-17 12:34:02','2019-09-17 12:34:02','a:9:{s:4:\"type\";s:16:\"flexible_content\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";i:0;s:17:\"conditional_logic\";i:0;s:7:\"wrapper\";